   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sl745a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>Knoxville</name>
                     <date>
                        <choice>
                           <orig>Aprile</orig>
                           <reg>April</reg>
                        </choice> 7th 1797</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I am <choice>
                  <orig>Doubtfull</orig>
                  <reg>Doubtful</reg>
               </choice> the prisoners is preparing to make their escape</p>
            <p>I am told they were heard <add>at work</add>Last night appearingly filing their Irons off </p>
            <p>I beg you to come over and examine them, and take the most <choice>
                  <orig>affectual</orig>
                  <reg>effectual</reg>
               </choice> means in your power to keep them secure in prison</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Your <choice>
                     <abbr>Hbl.</abbr>
                     <expan>Humble</expan>
                  </choice>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Servt.</abbr>
                     <expan>Servant</expan>
                  </choice>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name>John Sevier</name>
               </signed>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>Robert Housten</name>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Esqr.</abbr>
                        <expan>Esquire</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <add>Sheriff of <name>Knox <choice>
                        <abbr> Co</abbr>
                        <expan>County</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </name>
               </add>
               <pb n="2" facs="sl745b.small.jpg"/>
               <add>Sending out to different parts of the union for persons and papers in order to elucidate and facilitate the charges___</add>
               <salute>I am sir very respectfully <lb/>  your <choice>
                     <abbr>mo. obed.</abbr>
                     <expan>most obedient</expan>
                  </choice> servt.</salute>
               <pb n="3" facs="sl745c.small.jpg"/>
               <add>copy of a letter <lb/> to the <lb/> Sheriff of Knox <lb/> 7 April 1797 <lb/>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>No</abbr>
                     <expan>Number</expan>
                  </choice> 3</add>
               <add>Recorded</add>
            </closer>
         </div>
